The C/MS Music Card is shipped with I/O addresses set at 220 hex  to 22F  
hex.   You   need   to  re-install your  C/MS   Music   Card   and   the 
CMSDRV.COM   if  your system has any other adapter card using  the  same 
addresses.

Before   you  run the INSTALL program, you need to change   the   jumper 
setting on the C/MS music card to another address.

To run the INSTALL program, place your C/MS Master Disk in drive A:  and 
enter:
          INSTALL

